%% Trace: features/01-Email忘記密碼.feature
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant Ctrl as PasswordRecoveryController
    participant Svc as ForgotPasswordService
    participant Repo as MemberAuthRepository
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>FE: 忘記密碼 → 統一欄位輸入 Email + Captcha + 新密碼
    FE->>Ctrl: POST /forgot/mail (email, new_password, captcha)
    Ctrl->>Svc: resetByEmail(email, new_password)
    Svc->>Repo: findByEmailHash (is_deleted=false)
    Repo->>DB: SELECT
    DB-->>Repo: member_auth
    Repo-->>Svc: member_auth
    Svc->>Svc: hashPassword(new_password)
    Svc->>Repo: UPDATE member_auths SET password_hash, updated_at
    Repo->>DB: UPDATE
    Svc-->>Ctrl: ok
    Ctrl-->>FE: 200 OK
    FE-->>User: 提示「密碼已重設，請以新密碼登入」
